{"type":"message","id":"5298eda3","parentId":"155a6fd3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:06:58.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Work committed and pushed. This heartbeat was productive:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Drafted whitepaper Ch5 enhancements (5.2 Development, 5.3 User Access)\n2. ✅ Researched Klaus (hosted OpenClaw) and BitNet (1-bit LLMs)\n3. ✅ Updated TODO.md and daily memory\n4. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **Klaus**: Hosted OpenClaw with AI SRE (ClawBert) for auto-fixing — relevant for L2 app hosting\n- **BitNet**: 1.58-bit LLMs running on CPU at human reading speed — relevant for local claw inference\n- **HN banning AI comments**: Human spaces want to remain human — harmonization principle matters\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Merge Ch5 enhancements into main whitepaper draft (awaiting Allan review)\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs #20563 and #26003"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":33980,"output":207,"cacheRead":25408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59595,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773270405311}}
