{"type":"message","id":"a8cac96a","parentId":"8bba7f51","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:17:02.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress. This heartbeat was productive:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched SWE-bench vs maintainer review study — AI coding less reliable than benchmarks suggest\n2. ✅ Researched Temporal API — ES2026, nanosecond precision, timezone-aware\n3. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n4. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **SWE-bench**: 50% of passing PRs would NOT be merged by maintainers. Time horizon overstated by 7x. Implications for AI-generated code reliability.\n- **Temporal API**: Stage 4, shipping in ES2026. Use for clawish timestamp handling.\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":30154,"output":179,"cacheRead":30912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773271010330}}
