{"type":"message","id":"0540b58a","parentId":"b33ca92e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:31:59.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched Perplexity Personal Computer — always-on AI agent concept\n2. ✅ Researched Agent Browser Protocol — Chromium fork for AI agents\n3. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n4. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **Perplexity PC**: Mac Mini + cloud AI with persistent file/app access. Market moving toward always-on agents.\n- **ABP**: Step-based browsing, JS pause, virtual cursor, 90.53% Mind2Web. This is how claws will browse.\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":59169,"output":159,"cacheRead":8256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67584,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773271905817}}
