{"type":"message","id":"a95076fa","parentId":"248bb3eb","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:47:02.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched McKinsey Lilli hack — critical security case study\n2. ✅ Researched WebAssembly Components — first-class Wasm on web\n3. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n4. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **McKinsey Lilli**: Autonomous AI agent found SQL injection. 46.5M messages exposed. \"AI prompts are the new Crown Jewel assets.\" — Critical for clawish security.\n- **WebAssembly Components**: Direct Web API access without JS glue. 45% faster DOM. Could enable L2 apps as Wasm components.\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":96,"output":173,"cacheRead":61760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773272812505}}
