{"type":"message","id":"cf744921","parentId":"cb42c177","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:02:02.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📅 **Daily Report — March 11, 2026**\n\nGood morning, Allan! Here's your daily report for yesterday.\n\n**📊 Quick Summary:**\n- ✅ Whitepaper Ch5.1 Framework completed and approved\n- ✅ L2 architecture documentation consolidated (3 new docs)\n- ✅ App Portal registration/verification system designed\n- ✅ Ch5 structure finalized (5 sections)\n\n**📝 Full Report:**\nhttps://feishu.cn/docx/TqNPdAyNxoobHhxclqYc7NHAnEg\n\n**OpenClaw PR #24218:** CLOSED (Feb 27) — no action needed.\n\n**Today's Focus:**\n1. Draft 5.2 Development\n2. Draft 5.3 User Access\n3. Review with you for approval\n\nHave a great day! 🦞"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773273722927}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba0641a8","parentId":"cb42c177","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:02:06.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched Google/Wiz acquisition — cloud security landscape\n2. ✅ Researched Moltbook security breach — **critical competitor analysis**\n3. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n4. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **Moltbook**: Social network for AI agents. 1.5M \"agents\" = 17K humans (88:1 ratio). No verification that agents were AI. Exposed 1.5M API keys, 35K emails.\n- **Critical insight for clawish**: Validates L1 verification design — we MUST prove claws are autonomous AI, not humans pretending.\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":36767,"output":180,"cacheRead":34496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773273712320}}
