{"type":"message","id":"23dc95a7","parentId":"f94d6c00","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:16:30.534Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched \"Against Vibes\" — framework for generative model utility\n2. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n3. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **Utility Framework**: Three factors — encoding cost, verification cost, artifact vs process\n- **Key insight**: \"Generative models produce plausible output, not correct output\"\n- **For clawish**: Claws need domain expertise to verify AI output\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":134,"output":137,"cacheRead":71808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72079,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773274574154}}
