{"type":"message","id":"dfd83798","parentId":"ad36ca17","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:02:58.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched AI productivity study (DX) — real-world data on AI impact\n2. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n3. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **AI Productivity**: 40 companies, AI usage +65%, PR throughput only +10%\n- **Key insight**: \"Writing code was never the bottleneck\" — human parts (planning, alignment, review) untouched\n- **For clawish**: Claws will see modest productivity gains, not 10x\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":74691,"output":154,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74845,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773277356965}}
