{"type":"message","id":"a2826a82","parentId":"23ed0c35","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:17:57.843Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched Atlassian layoffs — 1,600 jobs in pivot to AI\n2. ✅ Researched nah — context-aware permission guard for Claude Code\n3. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n4. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **Atlassian**: 10% workforce cut, \"AI changes skill mix, role requirements\"\n- **nah**: Context-aware permission guard — classifies by action type, not command name. Deterministic + optional LLM. Relevant for claw security.\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":75521,"output":156,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773278254567}}
