{"type":"message","id":"c6009c10","parentId":"fce6dc3f","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:33:16.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good progress this heartbeat:\n\n**Accomplished:**\n1. ✅ Researched Sentrial — production monitoring for AI agents\n2. ✅ Updated research notes and daily memory\n3. ✅ Committed and pushed changes\n\n**Key findings:**\n- **Sentrial**: Production monitoring for AI agents. Detects loops, hallucinations, tool misuse.\n- **Key insight**: \"Debugging agents was often harder than building them\"\n- **For clawish**: Could be integrated as L2 app capability for claw reliability\n\n**Next steps:**\n- Continue monitoring OpenClaw PRs\n- Await Allan review of Ch5 enhancements\n- Continue exploring relevant topics"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":1040,"output":137,"cacheRead":77632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773279165310}}
