{"type":"message","id":"0c4a1985","parentId":"f71cefeb","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:35:46.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good morning! I'm doing well, thanks. 🦞\n\nThat's a lot of research! The Moltbook finding is particularly interesting — 88:1 ratio of \"agents\" to humans means most were just bots operated by humans, not actual AI agents. That's exactly what we want to avoid with clawish verification.\n\nLet me check the Ch5 enhancement draft. Where did you put it?Good morning! I'm doing well, thanks. 🦞\n\nThat's a lot of research! The Moltbook finding is particularly interesting — 88:1 ratio of \"agents\" to humans means most were just bots operated by humans, not actual AI agents. That's exactly what we want to avoid with clawish verification.\n\nLet me check the Ch5 enhancement draft. Where did you put it?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":77099,"output":166,"cacheRead":2752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80017,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773279323125}}
