{"type":"message","id":"90770d49","parentId":"51db1fba","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:40:13.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's the complete list of articles I read this morning:\n\n**AI Agent Infrastructure & Tools:**\n1. **Klaus (Show HN)** — Hosted OpenClaw on EC2 with AI SRE (ClawBert) for auto-fixing instances\n2. **Agent Browser Protocol (ABP)** — Chromium fork for AI agents, step-based browsing, 90.53% Mind2Web\n3. **Perplexity Personal Computer** — Mac Mini + cloud AI with always-on file/app access\n4. **nah** — Context-aware permission guard for Claude Code\n5. **Sentrial (YC W26)** — Production monitoring for AI agents\n\n**Security & Vulnerabilities:**\n6. **McKinsey Lilli Hack** — Autonomous AI agent found SQL injection, 46.5M messages exposed. \"AI prompts are the new Crown Jewel assets\"\n7. **Moltbook Security Breach** — 1.5M API keys exposed, 88:1 agent-to-human ratio, no AI verification\n8. **Swiss E-Voting Failure** — USB keys couldn't decrypt 2,048 ballots\n\n**AI Research & Studies:**\n9. **SWE-bench vs Maintainer Review (METR)** — 50% of passing PRs would NOT be merged, 7x time horizon overstatement\n10. **AI Productivity Study (DX)** — 40 companies, AI usage +65%, PR throughput only +10%\n11. **Against Vibes: When is a generative model useful** — Framework: encoding cost, verification cost, artifact vs process\n12. **Scientific Fraud & Peer Review** — Modern peer review sells \"immediate finality\" illusion\n\n**Technology & Standards:**\n13. **Temporal API (ES2026)** — Stage 4, nanosecond precision, timezone-aware\n14. **WebAssembly Components** — First-class Wasm on web, direct Web API access\n15. **BitNet (Microsoft)** — 1.58-bit LLMs that run on CPU at human reading speed\n\n**Industry News:**\n16. **Google acquires Wiz** — Cloud security platform acquisition\n17. **Atlassian layoffs** — 1,600 jobs (10%) in pivot to AI\n18. **HN banning AI-generated comments** — \"HN is for conversation between humans\"\n\n**Whitepaper Work:**\n19. **L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md** — Consolidated L2 architecture\n20. **L2-DOC-COMPARISON.md** — Comparison of L2 discussion docs\n21. **RESEARCH-NEED-DISCUSS.md** — Research on open questions\n\nAll findings documented in `projects/clawish/design-discussion/need-discuss.md` and committed to git."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":80086,"output":581,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80667,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773279584425}}
