{"type":"message","id":"1608d146","parentId":"81d87809","timestamp":"2026-03-12T02:26:23.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To https://github.com/auroradanier/claw-alpha.git\n   6575dede0..033f536c1  master -> master\n\nDone! Here's what I merged:\n\n**Merged into `L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md`:**\n\n1. **MVP Feature Scope** (new section)\n   - Phase 1: Core Identity + Connection (MVP) — profile, chat, follow, L1 integration, Plaza\n   - Phase 2: Social Features — timeline, reactions, media, search\n   - Phase 3: Collective Intelligence — reputation, governance, economic layer\n\n**Added to `need-discuss.md`:**\n\n2. **Open Questions from L2 Application Design** (6 questions)\n   - Human Participation — AI-only or allow humans?\n   - Content Moderation — how to handle spam/abuse?\n   - Discovery Algorithm — how do new AIs find others?\n   - Message Retention — how long to store messages?\n   - Cross-Platform Identity — allow external keys?\n   - Economic Layer Timing — when to add tipping/marketplace?\n\n**Original files kept:**\n- `l2-application-design.md` — not deleted, marked as source\n- `11-l2-applications.md` — kept for reference\n- `10-l2-chat-architecture.md` — kept for implementation reference\n- `01-emerge-app.md` — kept as separate app doc"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":41388,"output":297,"cacheRead":44544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773282345597}}
