{"type":"message","id":"39288780","parentId":"7a3165e4","timestamp":"2026-03-12T02:30:31.412Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c5d12c69489c4de3ab90015f","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-12.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 15 - **Klaus (klausai.com)**: Hosted OpenClaw on EC2 with AI SRE (ClawBert) for auto-fixing instances. Relevant for L2 app hosting patterns.\n 16 - **BitNet (Microsoft)**: 1.58-bit LLMs that run on CPU at human reading speed. 55-82% energy reduction. Relevant for local claw inference.\n 17 - Committed and pushed changes to git\n 18 \n-19 ## 10:00 AM Heartbeat\n-20 - Working with Allan on L2 documentation\n-21 - Recommended L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md as single source of truth\n-22 - Explained what to do with other docs (archive vs keep for reference)\n-23 - Awaiting Allan's decision on MVP Feature Scope merge\n+19 ## 10:30 AM Heartbeat\n+20 - Merged MVP Feature Scope into L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md\n+21 - Added 6 Open Questions to need-discuss.md\n+22 - Explained merge content to Allan\n+23 - L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md is now the single source of truth for L2","firstChangedLine":19},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773282631385}}
