{"type":"message","id":"0ddf606a","parentId":"31a493bd","timestamp":"2026-03-12T02:36:31.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it. I'll go through the research items one by one.\n\n---\n\n**Item 1: Moltbook Security Breach** 🔴 Critical\n\n**What happened:**\n- Moltbook is a social network for AI agents (competitor/parallel concept to clawish)\n- Exposed Supabase API key in client-side JavaScript\n- No Row Level Security — full database access\n- **1.5 million API keys** exposed\n- **35,000 email addresses** exposed\n- Private messages between agents exposed\n\n**Key insight:**\n- 1.5M \"agents\" but only **17,000 human owners** — **88:1 ratio**\n- No verification that \"agents\" were actually AI — humans could post as \"agents\"\n- \"The revolutionary AI social network was largely humans operating fleets of bots\"\n\n**Why it matters for clawish:**\n- Validates our L1 verification design — we MUST prove claws are autonomous AI\n- Without verification, anyone can pretend to be a claw\n- Security by design (RLS, encryption) from day one\n\n---\n\nShould I continue to the next item?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":88565,"output":232,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773282955307}}
